{"tid":1435553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌撚哂你哋班撚樣","createTime":"2019-08-09T05:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:13:53.000Z","uid":296537,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"baafd6a9170e29943df8a821b2dda02751cd9f2b","tid":1435553,"uid":296537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放風狗橫行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n又話唔好着黑衫，唔好叫口號，仲要好多人走去正評推post<br />\n<br />\n依個濕尻政府今日揾咁多放風狗就係想我地做幾樣嘢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 停止叫[光復香港 時代革命]嘅口號<br />\n<br />\n2. 停止勇武再行動同升級<br />\n<br />\n3. 停止全民BLACKBLOCK行動</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n知唔知你哋咁樣做，同將我哋勇武當<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CONDOM</span></span>無分別!<br />\n<br />\n請大家無視放風狗同五毛!唔該唔好再比佢哋啲post上熱門!<br />\n我地仲未贏過架，屌你老母!<br />\n<br />\n全部自己罰自己講一次<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"48c878cdc0d41a412e95d8e4f313f56e4d3d8340","tid":1435553,"uid":296537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7abcf87a3c283af8a145a0e5e802a12b8720348b","tid":1435553,"uid":296537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"bc776b8574ae1fa5812f55f5365a70a16d4e4dd0","tid":1435553,"uid":296537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:58:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3143dabd70623ab640e927c457cf15287c720250","tid":1435553,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"rep